c: 7
v: 85
t: "And to (the people of) Madyan, (We sent) their brother Shu`ayb. He said: \"O my people! Worship Allah! You have no other God but Him. Verily, a clear proof (sign) from your Lord has come unto you; so give full measure and full weight and wrong not men in their things, and do not do mischief on the earth after it has been set in order, that will be better for you, if you are believers"